snippet.title: Hot Springs | 温泉 (Onsen) - Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2401730/Hot_Springs___Onsen/

Step into the serene world of Onsen, where the warm embrace of Japanese hot springs meets the ultimate idle simulation experience. Find peace and relaxation as you create your own slice of paradise, while also connecting with others.
